# Billing Single Source of Truth

**BILLING RULE:** All pricing, trial, limits, and plan definitions MUST come from `app/billing/plan-config.ts`. No exceptions.

## Required pattern

```typescript
import { BILLING_CONFIG } from "~/billing/plan-config";
// or derive via billing-limits helpers (getCanonicalPlan, listCanonicalPlans, buildDbPlanSeedRecords)
```

## Never duplicate in other files

- Plan prices (`29`, `79`, `199`, `399`)
- `trialDays`
- Usage limits (`aiExecutions`, `automations`, `connectorSyncFrequencyHours`, `stores`)
- Feature flags (`executiveCOO`, `automationCenter`, `advancedAnalytics`)

## When adding or changing plans

1. Update `app/billing/plan-config.ts` only
2. Run `billing-config-consistency.test.ts`
3. Ensure Shopify Billing API charge amounts use `BILLING_CONFIG.plans`
4. Ensure UI displays prices from dashboard/plan helpers — never inline constants

## Validation

`billing-config-validator.ts` runs in non-production and throws on config drift (missing plans, duplicate prices, inconsistent trial days).
